data.description: This exceptional property boasts two spacious bedrooms and 2.5 modern baths in the desirable Stamford community. You'll love the upgrades throughout the home, especially the stunning kitchen with custom features, top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, gorgeous granite countertops with matching backsplash, elegant self-closing wooden cabinets, a convenient built-in pantry, and a coffee bar for your morning routine. The bathrooms and kitchen have been meticulously designed with attention to detail, creating a unique and impressive living space. The house has been beautifully tiled and carpeted and hosts three renovated bathrooms with new showers, vanities, and lighting. Enjoy the added safety and comfort of new impact windows, a newer AC(2022), and a new roof(2023)! The HOA includes outside insurance, internet, community pool, landscaping, and garbage service. Located conveniently close to schools and shopping, this home is move-in ready and waiting for you to make it your own.
